We’re back with more chestnut fun!! The holiday season is upon us and so we’re celebrating with a wintery giveaway full of LUCK. Guess how many CHESTNUTS are in the Sweet Craft cup for a chance to win a case of our newest most spirited flavor, EGGNOG PANNA COTTA 🌰🌰🌰

To enter:
* Follow us + like this post
* Guess how many chestnuts are in the closed cup
* DM us your guess
* Tag a festive friend for additional entries, one entry per comment

Giveaway ends December 16th at 11:59pm PST
Winners will be drawn the following day and contacted after.
Winners get a case of Eggnog Panna Cotta!!

This giveaway is not affiliated with Instagram or Meta.
